<P>THE SHEEP-SHEARING: A DRAMATIC PASTORAL. IN THREE ACTS. TAKEN FROM SHAKESPEARE. As it is performed at the THEATRE ROYAL IN THE HAY-MARKET.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed for G. KEARSLY, No. 46, FLEET-STREET. M,DCC,LXXVII.</P>
